latestPosts.caption: Feeling incredibly grateful yet slightly jittery as I sit down to write this post. 😅 Next week, LittleBox will be stepping into the spotlight on Shark Tank, and the emotions are running high! 🦈✨ It’s been a whirlwind journey filled with late nights, countless pitches, and a whole lot of heart. I’m so thankful for every member of our team who has poured their blood, sweat, and tears into making our dream a reality. 💪🏼 And to our loyal supporters, your unwavering belief in us means the world. 🌎 As we gear up for the big moment, I can’t help but feel a mix of excitement, nerves, and a dash of anticipation. Whatever happens, I know we’ve already won in so many ways. Let’s do this, LittleBox fam! 💼🚀 #Gratitude #SharkTankReady #MixedFeelings #LittleBox

We did it! 1 MILLION orders and counting! 🎉

A huge THANK YOU to all our amazing customers for making this journey unforgettable. As a proud brand from the North East, we’ve faced roadblocks along the way, but we’re committed to solving them and providing a smooth experience for you all. Our goal is to create a perfect, no-wastage, no-inventory sustainable model — doing our bit for the environment, one box at a time.

We’re just getting started, and we couldn’t have reached this milestone without your love and support. Keep the orders coming – we’re ready for more!
